x%2Fi%2FbWZuZRk.jpg&h=6ade4135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSbQKh1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSbQKh1.jpg&h=732a5881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.25 荃葵青大遊行 </span></span><br />\n時間：14:30（集會）15:00（遊行隊伍出發）<br />\n起點：葵芳（南）巴士總站 ( 啱啱改咗 )<br />\n終點：荃灣公園<br />\n遊行路線：葵芳南總站-&gt;經行人隧道往葵福路（南行）天橋-&gt;橫跨興芳路-&gt;落行人天橋近葵福路（北行）-&gt;葵福路（北行）-&gt;葵福路與德士古道交界横過行人路處上行人天橋-&gt;橫過德士古道-&gt;落行人天橋近德士古道（北行）-&gt;楊屋道（西行）-&gt;入荃灣公園廣場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGz62yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGz62yb.jpg&h=d03a6e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFVVaYD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFVVaYD.gif&h=1712aec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong><br />\n撤回逃犯條例<br />\n撤銷暴動定性<br />\n釋放被捕義士<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n實行雙真普選<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b50cc6891f5ebc25f621fe16d77156c5528a6122","tid":1488654,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔係唔俾你J大波madam, 不過J完就好做正經野啦, 推下黎824 825遊行post啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2a1166b016be9dc8b5a16cc680baad7d5b69936","tid":1488654,"uid":180466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d8879f09ab167fd695cb5b718fa1ac1936da244","tid":1488654,"uid":180466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:18:50.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"55291acd06c7044d7b605357534bdea2ece46dbf","tid":1488654,"uid":180466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa307ea3af5d0ede5c59cf60e41bf73ff8345f5","tid":1488654,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"